data.name: description2.Text
data.value: Brighten their day with a touch of Mauve Magic, with a bouquet of blossoms radiating fondness and affection. Featuring a bunch of soft purple blooms, accented with sprays of lush foliage, this charming mini bouquet is a sweet and simple way to convey your love and best wishes.

data.name: Label9.Text
data.value: We know how forgetful we can be during our anniversary. For that last-minute anniversary gift, get a unique bouquet. Add in chocolates, cake, a balloon, and have it delivered to your home on the same day with our same-day delivery. Order from our collection below.

data.name: description4.Text
data.value: Arranged with bounties of pretty pink roses, carnations, gerberas, with sprays of white aster and papua - our Pixie flower bouquet is the perfect gift to send your heartfelt wishes, full of magic to your loved one.

data.name: description3.Text
data.value: Bright, bold, and and beyond beautiful - our Helia flower bouquet with luminous red roses, sunflowers, and sprays of white statice make for the perfect bouquet worthy of the brightest of celebrations.
